{"tid":869227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本首隻怪獸獲殊榮     NASA命名新星座「哥斯拉座」","createTime":"2018-10-20T07:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T09:42:46.000Z","uid":1221,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8770ac2b97eb9f14291ce9fc2a26e7b7f48ee1f4","tid":869227,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201810/20181018ffaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201810%2F20181018ffaf.jpg&h=745e6d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署（NASA）公布，以日本殿堂級怪獸「哥斯拉」為新星座冠名。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「哥斯拉座」是由NASA與世界多個研究機構，透過費米伽瑪射線空間望遠鏡，觀測到會散發「伽瑪射線暴」（Gamma Ray Burst）的星體連成的星座。因為外型出奇地似怪獸噴射高熱射線，就將其命名為「哥斯拉座」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/thumbnails/image/grconstellationsnorthfermifullsizefinal.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2Fgrconstellationsnorthfermifullsizefinal.gif&h=68ebcc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNASA指哥斯拉是日本的著名怪獸及流行文化標誌，牠的必殺技高熱射線與星體釋出的伽馬射線也相當類似。而「哥斯拉座」的伽馬射線，則主要來自活躍星系核（active galactic nucleus）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是次NASA一共發表22個新星座，除了「哥斯拉」外，還有「富士山」、「變形俠醫」（Hulk）、「小王子」、星空奇遇記「企業號星艦」、「愛因斯坦」、「鬥獸場」、雷神索爾的武器鎚「妙爾尼爾」（Mj&ouml;lnir）、甚至連「費米望遠鏡衛星」自己也成為了星座。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/godzilla_jp/status/1052881475224231937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgodzilla_jp%2Fstatus%2F1052881475224231937&d=CUqz8Jvto69YGFgxZhJLbmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9c9fe069\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgodzilla_jp%2Fstatus%2F1052881475224231937&h=9b08f70f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/godzilla_jp/status/1052881475224231937</a>"},{"pid":"7b173f834c4990c8f33ae206684c63b21ce8ce93","tid":869227,"uid":216409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8770ac2b97eb9f14291ce9